    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This car is in good condition and has been well cared for, making it a great choice for your next vehicle. It offers a smooth driving experience and a clean interior, with only minor signs of use that reflect its well-maintained history. Ready to drive home today!",
